at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.stm32

Class RMCSAdvancedComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.stm32.RMCSAdvancedComponent

  • public abstract class RMCSAdvancedComponent
extends java.lang.Object
    A composition of RMCSControlComponent and RMCSSensorComponent. Sub-classes of RMCSAdvancedComponent are both able to process IControlData and post SensorData.
    Author:
    Boeck
